                                        //shr_f(url);
                                        Feb 12, 201912:09 (IST)--> Prime Minister Narendra Modi has rock-solid support of people ahead of the coming Lok Sabha election, BJP president Amit Shah claimed today. "I travel the country... I can see that people are standing with Prime Minister Narendra Modi like a rock and one can see the support in their eyes," Mr Shah said addressing BJP workers.
